OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for at least 20
OL,8,Fyears after beating a "kind and
OL,9,Fgentle" pensioner to death after being
OL,10,Fconfronted for hanging around elderly
OL,11,Fresidents' flats.
OL,13,FPhillip Fraczek, then aged 20, sparked
OL,14,Falarm as he tried several door handles
OL,15,Fat the flats in Plaistow Road, West
OL,16,FHam, at lunchtime on May 15 2024.
OL,18,FHe fell asleep on the floor, and just
OL,19,Fover an hour later, 79-year-old
OL,20,FFranklin Agbotui woke him and asked
OL,21,Fhim to leave.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
