FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,FNeighbours then heard banging noises
OL,8,Fand screams coming from the
OL,9,Fpensioner's flat.
OL,11,FHe was found badly injured and
OL,12,Fsurrounded by broken furniture, and
OL,13,Fdied five days later in hospital.
OL,15,FPolish national Fraczek was tackled by
OL,16,Fpolice officers two streets away,
OL,17,Fheadbutting one in the jaw as they
OL,18,Farrested him.
OL,20,FHis knuckles and Nike trainers were
OL,21,Fcovered in Mr Agbotui's blood.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,FFraczek, now 22, of no fixed address,
OL,8,Fwas jailed for life with a minimum of
OL,9,F20 years and four months at
OL,10,FSnaresbrook Crown Court on Monday,
OL,11,Fhaving admitted murder and assault of
OL,12,Fan emergency worker at an earlier
OL,13,Fhearing.
OL,15,FDetective Superintendent Kelly Allen
OL,16,Fsaid: "Franklin was known to friends
OL,17,Fand neighbours as a kind and gentle
OL,18,Fman, often seen tending the flowers in
OL,19,Ftheir shared garden.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,F"He had a long and successful career
OL,8,Fin the Merchant Navy and had earned a
OL,9,Fhappy retirement.
OL,11,F"This was horrifically taken from him
OL,12,Fby Fraczek ` whose unprovoked and
OL,13,Fsavage attack has rocked this
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank the Met
OL,17,Fofficers who put themselves in harm's
OL,18,Fway to chase down Fraczek and detain
OL,19,Fhim, bringing him immediately into
OL,20,Fcustody and preserving vital evidence.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,F"Our thoughts remain with Franklin's
OL,8,Ffamily and friends, and hope the
OL,9,Flengthy sentence can bring them some
OL,10,Fdegree of peace."
OL,12,FHis family said in their victim impact
OL,13,Fstatement: "Our father lived a quiet,
OL,14,Fhumble life grounded in integrity,
OL,15,Frespect, perseverance, education and
OL,16,Ffaith.
OL,18,F"He instilled these values in us
OL,19,Fconsistently and led by example.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@QO]uD@LOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,F"Despite his modest nature, he was
OL,8,Fdeeply present in our lives ` offering
OL,9,Fguidance, checking in regularly and
OL,10,Fsending daily messages.
OL,12,F"He was a constant, steady source of
OL,13,Fsupport.
OL,15,F"Beyond our immediate family, he was
OL,16,Fan active and valued member of his
OL,17,Fchurch community, where his absence
OL,18,Fhas also been keenly felt.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,F"We continue to feel the absence of
OL,8,Four father's kindness, his humour and
OL,9,Fhis guidance.
OL,11,F"The regular contact and reassurance
OL,12,Fhe provided are no longer there,
OL,13,Fleaving a void in our daily lives.
OL,15,F"His death has had a profound and far-
OL,16,Freaching impact on our wellbeing, our
OL,17,Fsense of stability and our family as a
OL,18,Fwhole.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
