CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777468273
OL,3,C'Kind and gentle' pensioner beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath after confronting would-be
OL,5,Cintruder
OL,7,F"The consequences ` emotional,
OL,8,Fpractical and long term ` remain
OL,9,Fongoing, and we continue to navigate
OL,10,Flife without the presence and support
OL,11,Fthat defined his role in our lives."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
